Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.15,0:00:09.15,Default,,0,0,0,,MERIDIAN. Climate-resilience watch over MARFORPAC supply lines.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.15,0:00:14.15,Default,,0,0,0,,LOGCOM problem set: contested logistics, supply chain, expeditionary\Nops.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.15,0:00:19.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Twelve critical nodes — Guam to Okinawa to CNMI to the Philippines.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.16,0:00:25.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Thirty NOAA, JTWC, FEMA, and G-4 reports stream in — no data movement.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.16,0:00:31.16,Default,,0,0,0,,A multi-step LLM agent scores all twelve nodes — structured JSON.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.19,0:00:39.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Then a Kamiwaza-deployed model drafts a USMC OPORD-style\Nfive-paragraph brief.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.49,0:00:41.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Top-3 named threats. Recommended COA per CCDR. One page.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.49,0:00:47.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Inject a new incident — re-rank the chain in seconds.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.50,0:00:54.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Set KAMIWAZA_BASE_URL and the same code runs inside the wire.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.51,0:01:02.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Powered by the Kamiwaza Stack. Deploy in hours, not months.
